  "settings.app.intro_html": {
    "message": "Spotify 要求每个应用都注册自己的 <strong>Client ID</strong>。在 <a href=\"https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard\">developer.spotify.com/dashboard</a> 免费创建一个（点击 <em>Create app</em>，随意命名，勾选 <em>Web API</em>）。将 <code>http://127.0.0.1:8080/spotify/callback</code> 添加为 Redirect URI——端口任意，Spotify 只需要填一个。复制它给你的 Client ID 并粘贴到下方。",
    "description": "Settings: app setup instructions",
    "_machine_translated": true,
